 sake (and to avoid soggy dances later), are light yet fulfilling options that can also be dressed up with avocado or grilled chicken. \n- Fresh fruit smoothies offer a burst of vitamins and flavor, ideal if you're seeking something hydrating post rehearsal!  \nRemember to enjoy foods in moderation – balancing your diet is key for sustaining energy throughout our dance practices too!", 'components': [], 'channel_type': 0, 'channel_id': '1272275698060365898', 'author': {'username': 'funktion bot v1', 'public_flags': 0, 'primary_guild': None, 'id': '1272269221753258085', 'global_name': None, 'display_name_styles': None, 'discriminator': '0160', 'collectibles': None, 'clan': None, 'bot': True, 'avatar_decoration_data': None, 'avatar': '24981c3646c8c068e7b3a5453bec29bc'}, 'attachments': [], 'guild_id': '374311259836776468'}}
